text: Kim Dong-young () is a Korean name consisting of the family name Kim and the given name Dong-young, and may also refer to: * Kim Dong-young (racewalker) (born 1980), South Korean athlete * Kim Dong-young (actor) (born 1988), South Korean actor * Kim Dong-young (singer) (born 1996), South Korean singer
title: Kim Dong-young
